trans-unit.source: Identifies Windows cryptographic object identifier (OID) groups.
trans-unit.target: Identifica grupos OID (Identificador de Objeto Criptográfico) do Windows.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Oid.FromOidValue%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Esta enumeração é usada pelo método <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Oid.FromOidValue%2A>.
